Its an Office Death Match scenario. This is a 2nd remake of the first one i made. I have added some more props and decals.. and lights. so it is not full bright anymore. I added windows in the spawn areas. Some areas were slightly remade too.

This is the 2nd map i have mad so be kind with feedback haha. This is the final of this map. I might make another map if i get a good idea.
